Service.create!(name: 'Wellness Program + Meal Plan', description: 'EFT and Matrix Re-imprinting can create significant shifts in your life. It allows you to identify any blocks preventing you from living from a place of joy. These techniques are used to release the past so you can move in a positive direction. We will identify existing belief systems or negative memories that limit you from living your most authentic life.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 90, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 6)
Service.create!(name: 'Astrology Reading for Self-awareness', description: 'EFT is an amazing tool to reduce cortisol levels (stress hormone) and our stress response (fight/flight). When adrenaline kicks in, it causes fear/anxiety to take over of bodies/minds. We will tap together to "turn down the volume" of the stress response. Tapping has a direct and immediate effect on parts of the brain that control fight/flight.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 40, duration: 105, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 7)
Service.create!(name: 'Taro Intuitive Reading', description: 'This is a 15 to 30 minute instructional meditation video. I assign each meditation based on the student’s needs. This can also be a preview of my teaching style for a longer 90-minute yoga & meditstion class or private session. You will also have access to an email question and answer session with me to answer your questions about the class.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 45, duration: 120, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 7)
Service.create!(name: 'Biofield Tuning & Human Design Reading', description: 'The main purpose of the session is to create a safe, peaceful environment in which the client can mindfully focus on their breath and movement as a form of meditation. The yoga session will start with an assessment of the client\'s well being to create an individualized practice. There will be a strong emphasis on breathing techniques throughout the session.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 70, duration: 135, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 8)
Service.create!(name: 'Somatic Therapy For Collective, Intergenerational & Karmic Trauma', description: 'The wellness assessment is the initial session to have the opportunity to get to know the client in a comprehensive way. This can be done both in person or virtually (video conference). I will convey that as an Adult Nurse Practitioner I would like to be an adjunct to their medical care and provide education and resources to help them navigate their health.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 75, duration: 150, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 8)
Service.create!(name: 'Biotherapy 101', description: 'At the time of an appointment with my clients, I will be conducting either a computerized or paper assessment. there is one assessment for personal training/group fitness and their is one assessment for wellness coaching. in my personal training and group fitness assessments, their will be general questions, that I will ask my clients to answer based on their level of knowledge that they have on their own personal health and fitness level.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 80, duration: 165, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 9)
Service.create!(name: 'Healing with Biotherapy', description: 'A Holistic Health Coach is a guide and mentor who empowers you, and provides ongoing support and guidance as you set goals and make sustainable changes that improve your health and happiness. As your Holistic Health Coach, Melanie offers a support system that is unique to your needs.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 100, duration: 180, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 9)
Service.create!(name: 'Optimal Breathing', description: 'I practice intuitive and integrative bodywork. I work with clients to customize sessions based on their needs and goals of the session. I combine various techniques from my toolkit to provide unique therapeutic bodywork sessions that aid the body\'s innate ability to heal itself. I incorporate swedish, shiatsu, acupressure, energy work and essential oils.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 45, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 10)
Service.create!(name: 'Breathwork & Meditation', description: 'We\'ll discuss your current health status, health issues that are challenging you, and set up a nutritional plan to address the underlying causes. Using targeted nutrients, finding triggers, and adding in specific foods, you\'ll come away with a number of recommendations for diet and lifestyle to start you on your way toward greater health. Practical tips and strategies make simple shifts will be given and customized to your needs.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 90, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 10)
Service.create!(name: '60 min Business & Mindset Coaching Session', description: 'These 4 sessions will provide you with thorough education, support, meal plans, lifestyle tips, and accountability over a 2 month period. Suggested for those looking to heal more chronic issues and looking to make long-lasting changes. Specific recommendations and plans will be created just for your health needs and goals.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 40, duration: 60, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 11)
Service.create!(name: 'Business Mind Training', description: 'During your first appointment, we create larger goals in a variety of different areas in your life and discuss when we want these accomplished. We discuss what barriers you often face and how to hurdle them. We reflect on your strengths. Together we will come up with our first stepping stone for those bigger goals. You will be held accountable throughout the week to these goals.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 45, duration: 30, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 11)
Service.create!(name: 'Symptoms Related Biotherapy Session', description: 'I create coaching packages designed specifically for the client. Based on your specific needs, we will work together to create a road map of success. Packages range from monthly to annually and are priced accordingly.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 45, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 12)
Service.create!(name: '60 min 1-1 Reiki Energy Healing', description: 'This is an introductory yoga session tailored to your needs.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 70, duration: 75, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 12)
Service.create!(name: 'Online Pro Wellness Program', description: 'Are your aware that your mind is highly hackable? Today is your day to learn everything you need to know to make sure you control what\'s going through your mind & what you are creating for your future. Have you wondered why you keep repeating the same patterns? Yes, your subconscious mind & beliefs are making things happen for you.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 50, duration: 30, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 13)
Service.create!(name: 'Online Fitness Training', description: 'Like a network of rivers nourishing a landscape, the meridians are the channels through which “Qi” flows, to nourish and energize the human body. These channels exist within the subtle body and returns the body to a state of equilibrium and wellness.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 45, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 13)
Service.create!(name: 'Symptoms-tailored Consultation Using Functional Medicine', description: 'A balanced body encourages balanced thinking. An organic body that functions well results in intelligent evolution. Yoga encourages a skillful means of developing balance, strength and depth. A tool to learn more about the Self and the world.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 80, duration: 75, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 14)
Service.create!(name: 'Healing with Functional Medicine', description: 'Chiropractic appointments will include a full spinal and musckuloskeltal assessment. Soft tissue therapies in various forms including percussion therapy, cupping, and myofascial releases will be delivered if deemed necessary. Spinal manipulation and corrective exercises will follow.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 15, duration: 120, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 14)
Service.create!(name: 'Herbal Treatment', description: 'In the Mind Body Collective, we will discuss how the attention and direction of the mind can affect the physical body. Sessions will begin with a lengthly emotional health history. We will take time to identify what may be ailing the mind and in turn affecting the body.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 90, duration: 135, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 15)
Service.create!(name: 'Herbal medicine 101', description: 'Functional Medicine sessions vary based on the patient. Anything from fatigue, gastrointestinal difficulties, thyroid dysfunction, autoimmune, and headaches may be treated with functional medicine.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 35, duration: 180, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 15)
Service.create!(name: 'Life Cycle Readings (Life Cycle Analysis-Professional Training)', description: 'Reiki is a natural universal energy that permeates all beings. In this session we will work to channel the energy towards its highest good in you and encourage self healing.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 150, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 16)
