Service.create!(name: 'Discover Previous Life', description: 'In this phone call, Skype session, or Zoom call, we’ll discuss your health history and I’ll recommend what I think would work best for your specific needs. We\'ll discuss your eating habits, lifestyle changes, and more.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 30, duration: 60, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 17)
Service.create!(name: 'Hypnotherapy To Connect With Your Inner childhood trauma', description: 'During the INITIAL HEALTH + LIFESTYLE COACHING SESSION, together we assess your health history, nutrition, daily habits, current fitness practice, discuss challenges, and establish goals. Sessions following the initial consultation are focused on support and accountability. For lasting lifestyle changes and results, it is recommended to commit to a 3 MONTH PROGRAM meeting weekly or a 6 MONTH PROGRAM meeting bi-weekly.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 45, duration: 45, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 17)
Service.create!(name: 'Sleep like a baby', description: 'Beginners Vinyasa Yoga Flow is an introduction to the core elements of vinyasa yoga (linking breath with each movement between poses). We walk through a step-by-step of basic warm-up poses, vinyasa flows, foundational poses, restorative poses, and breath work, with light meditation if preferred. I\'m happy to provide hands-on assists if that is something you are comfortable with.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 100, duration: 135, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 18)
Service.create!(name: 'Better Sleep Better Life', description: 'Intermediate Yoga Vinyasa Flow provides experience yogis with a deeper level of asana modifications, mixed within a vinyasa flow. You can choose which poses you\'re working towards that you\'d like me to incorporate, or I can provide my own after assessing your flow. Common intermediate poses include headstand, tripod, binds, one-legged balancing poses, scorpion, wheel, crow variations, and more. This session is all about fun and non-judgement.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 35, duration: 90, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 18)
Service.create!(name: 'Elevate Journey: Transform Pain Into Your Superpower', description: 'The Breath Work Session focuses on how our how controlled breathing can help to relax the body and mind and allow for a deeper yoga practice. You can choose to do a full breathing session, or one that links with poses or where your mind is at on that specific day. Please see below for a more detailed description of each breath. Ocean-like nostril breathing (Ujjayi): The foundational breathing technique for vinyasa yoga.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 60, duration: 105, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 19)
Service.create!(name: 'Life Changes Discovery Coaching Session', description: 'Touch deprivation can feel like loneliness, stress and a sense of missing something. During a Platonic Therapeutic Touch Session you will enter a nonjudgmental and caring container. Through holding space you will have the opportunity to experience vulnerability, intimacy, self-awareness and touch.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 65, duration: 90, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 19)
Service.create!(name: 'Peaceful Moment in Life', description: 'Maybe you need to blow off a little steam and vent about a problem. Perhaps you are looking for understanding and want to share about a situation. Or, simply, you want to be heard and acknowledged. Now, what if your schedule does not allow for an in-person session? This is a quick and easy way to connect with a practitioner when you cannot make it in for a healing hug.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 25, duration: 30, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 20)
Service.create!(name: 'Meditation in Forest', description: 'We offer guided meditation and deep relaxation. Options for meditation include restorative stretch and meditation, sitting meditation, full body scan meditation, self-kindness meditation, guided meditation to music, or seated meditation in silence. Our spaces are designed for optimum relaxation and focus.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 30, duration: 45, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 20)
Service.create!(name: 'Lactation Support', description: 'RapidSculpt EMS is a 20 minute total body strength and endurance training program followed by a 10 minute muscle recovery program. The entire session takes approximately 45 minutes. Clients must bring athletic shoes, water and a face towel. FireSnake Fitness provides the specialized training suit that must be worn during the training.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 15, duration: 60, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 21)
Service.create!(name: 'Pregnancy wellness', description: 'FireSculpt is a 35-minute total-body strength training class that uses dumbbells, body-weight and cardio bursts to tone and sculpt the body. All movements are synced to music which makes it incredibly fun! Modifications are offered for almost all exercises so that all clients can achieve success, no matter their fitness level or limitations. Virtual classes are $20/class.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 100, duration: 120, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 21)
Service.create!(name: 'Is your table healthy?', description: 'We begin each session with a check in as to where you are in your cycle or treatment journey. We discuss what and where you would like to focus of the session to be, and move into a series of restorative poses to fully benefit your reproductive health. We end the session with a meditation focused on what we have worked on, where we are, and where you want to be moving forward.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 35, duration: 135, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 22)
Service.create!(name: 'Nutrition & Lifestyle Coaching', description: 'I am here to hold the space for you as you grow into this new role of parent. I hear and see the challenges you face with physical and emotional discomforts of pregnancy and the postpartum period. I offer prenatal yoga sessions to help bring more ease to your body and mind and preparing you for a more comfortable pregnancy and helping you heal and strengthen postpartum.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 50, duration: 180, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 22)
Service.create!(name: 'Optimizing hormonal balance', description: 'The above price represents a 4 session package of 1 - on - 1 spiritually bold mentorship, that decodes life\'s invisible obstacles through ancestral mediumship, identifying dream & personality patterning through intersectional behavioral breath and embodied techniques. Lastly postural and core awareness support through tailored goal planning. Most clients work with me for a minimum to three to six months on an intended goal.', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 30, duration: 30, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 23)
Service.create!(name: 'Naturopathic Medicine', description: 'The first few sessions are focused on learning the breathing technique while doing introductory movements on the reformer. Breath first, Body second. During these sessions a person becomes aware of using sensory perception to tell the Brain how to adjust the Body to create proper form. It can be considered as a physically active form of meditation.', service_type: 'In-person', price: 40, duration: 30, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 23)
Service.create!(name: 'Rapid Transformational Therapy 101', description: 'The Pilates session is for the specific needs of the runner, which will improve their performance and running technique to prevent injuries, thus strengthening the deep muscles associated with running', service_type: 'Virtual', price: 45, duration: 60, active: true, practitioner_specialty_id: 24)
